      <title><![CDATA[CSS笔记]]></title>
      <url>https://uyong.github.io/2016/07/02/css%E7%AC%94%E8%AE%B0/</url>
      <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h3 id="CSS语法"><a href="#CSS语法" class="headerlink" title="CSS语法"></a>CSS语法</h3><figure class="highlight css"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line"><span class="selector-tag">selector</span>&#123;</div><div class="line">    <span class="attribute">key</span>:value;</div><div class="line">    <span class="attribute">key</span>:value;</div><div class="line">&#125;</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h4 id="示例：对所有的body标签使用该样式"><a href="#示例：对所有的body标签使用该样式" class="headerlink" title="示例：对所有的body标签使用该样式"></a>示例：对所有的body标签使用该样式</h4><figure class="highlight css"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div><div class="line">7</div><div class="line">8</div><div class="line">9</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line"><span class="selector-tag">body</span> &#123;</div><div class="line">  <span class="attribute">color</span>: <span class="number">#000</span>;</div><div class="line">  <span class="attribute">margin</span>: <span class="number">0</span>;</div><div class="line">  <span class="attribute">font-family</span>: Georgia, Palatino, serif;</div><div class="line">&#125;</div><div class="line">将继承<span class="selector-tag">body</span>中的其他属性(继承存在浏览器兼容性问题)</div><div class="line"><span class="selector-tag">p</span>, <span class="selector-tag">td</span>, <span class="selector-tag">ul</span>, <span class="selector-tag">ol</span>&#123;</div><div class="line">    <span class="attribute">color</span>: <span class="number">#ffffff</span>;</div><div class="line">&#125;</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<ol>
<li>派生选择器<br><code>h2 strong { color:#000000; }</code></li>
<li>ID选择器<br><code>#idname { key : value; }</code><br><code>#idname td { key : value; }</code></li>
<li>类选择器<br><code>.classname { key : value; }</code><br><code>td.classname { key : value; }</code><br><code>.classname td { key : value; }</code><br><code>.cn1.cn2 { key : value; }</code></li>
<li>属性选择器<br><code>[type=&quot;text&quot;] { key : value; }</code><br><code>input[type=&quot;text&quot;] { key : value; }</code></li>
</ol>
]]></content>
